Description: NUX - Production-Grade Linux CLI Manager
 NUX is a comprehensive CLI for Linux system administration,
 offering real-time monitoring, disk management, security auditing,
 service and network management, AI agent integration, and more.
 Designed for DevOps and SREs requiring idempotent operations.
